messages.content: nobody in the server is a floridian lol

Day 1. This is a new place, and odd place too. I only have one companion, ash. But he’s rarely alive. I regret that your mom joke but it is what it is, I will be used to it soon. Besides, this will be my home for a long time, almost forever, I might never leave. I don’t see a way to escape but I’ll look tomorrow. -E

I’ve only spent 40 minutes up here… or down here. I cannot tell. It’s been a horribly boring time. There is quite nothing to do but count bricks they make up the walls. Quite boring. I can barely survive 40 minutes. How am I supposed to survive longer? Also there is sadly no sleep medication. I would ask a warden for one but @Squid is the only one. He hasn’t came by a single time. This will be quite the lonely time. At most I can hope for sleep deprivation to kill me. Food and water just kinda *poof* into existence. It’s happend only one time. It was quite the sight to see. -E

Day 2, well after several hours I managed to fall asleep. I woke up to more food and water. I isn’t know how it’s possible. But it did came with an spoon for this soupish like thing. It made a small dent in the wall but it like disappears with the food treys. It’s really weird. I have no freinds here and only concrete floor. A single lightbulb. And walls, not a single window. I’m starting to suffer from altitude sickness, or I’m just homesick. Probably both. -E

I just woke up, it’s horrible. Several phones taped to the walls, its horrible, it’s just playing plushy videos. It’s quite interesting when you don’t look at the plushies, the back round is cool. But I tried to take Em down, they were stuck.
Oh god, there are more, it’s scary. I will keep writing if I see more. -E
Day 3, the wardens are quite rude here. About what you’d expect, correcting my grammar, spelling, it’s bad. And there are more plushie things. -E
Well this is quite odd, I suppose another friend is a robot.
I was talking about owo bot.
It’s been a couple days, I can play blackjack, it’s better than nothing.
It will keep me entertained, but the wardens are still rude. Pep and squid. -E
I don’t know how it happens but somehow the warden just changed how they look, I can believe it’s plastic surgery or were in a simulation. -E

I no longer know how long I’ve been in here. I just sleep when I’m tired, there’s really no way for me to tell. I don’t know if even any will every see me or these writings again. I think I know a way out. I’ll have to learn how to lock pick. On my own.
Welp, I’m hiding my writings from now on
Welp I’ve hidden everything I had under a loose floorboard. Under it it’s just concrete, can’t tunnel out anymore. I think maybe something with the roof or just the main door. -E
Well, I forgot to address what I have, I have a small paper clip, and some paper and a pen. I was writing when I was transported. It’s been a while sense I’ve written.
I’ve been granted, back to my clan. More lively there.
Welp, it was nice to be there. Just for a second. I got more paper.
I actually feel quite peace of mind here, it’s a nice place to think. No distractions, no loud noises, and it’s just quiet. I’m actually starting to enjoy it here, -E
In starting to feel homesick, just thinking about the pleasures of the outside world. Are my freinds and family dead? Will i ever see them Again? I suppose it’s up to fate.
I believe I will die here, I’m not going to eat my food. I will die eventually. -E
When I get back home of corse
Wait aren’t I’m supposed to write like journal entrees right
Can you delete all of those

Welp I had some freedom for a second. I was even downloading pictures to post. That I drew of course. It would’ve been fun. I can’t change it sadly. Sadly death is not an option. I will spend eternity here, perhaps I’ll try my silver tongue to convince them to let me out. -E
If I do can I get out of my eternal prison

I would like to schedule a teleconference to see if I could possibly leave and into house arrest. I would be trapped but I’d have company. Sadly it won’t work. They wouldn’t let me schedule a teleconference. Shame. -E
Well turns out a warden had some stream, I don’t know what it was about but I sure missed it. To busy playing solitaire on my solar powered I pod. -E
It was a bloody great stream
I'll send you the link to it
you can see it even tho it ended
Bro I didn’t bring my laptop to Africa
That was a waste of space

Today I discovered something. It’s called photic sneeze reflex. Basically you sneeze when your in a bright area. It only effects 17 to like 35% of people. I’m also pretty sure it’s a kinda of mutation. Does that mean I’m an X-Men? -E
Do you suppose you could make my prison public
Well I’m here. It’s been a while. There isn’t much to write about. I’ve had these journal entrees forever.  I don’t know what to do with them -E
It’s been a long time, perhaps I’ll talk to the wardens for a release, it won’t happen though. I’m stuck here. -E
How long is my sentance here
Can o get released next week
I’ve been in here for over 2 months
Am o back on the server
No the score was "yes" at 0 and "no" at 5
You told me to send a sceenshot
I check discord 4 times a day and this is my last time today, but I’ll ping you asking everyday for every time I get on from now on
I thought I got to the end of my sentance
Why must I be in here again
ask pep, I wasn't the one that put you in
no you didn't ive never seen you use a period
